name: CoreAPI Run_Launchpad
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Run_Launchpad
about:
Description

Planet 9-Run_Launchpad maintains the planet 9 Launchpads.

API Run_Launchpad is the API to access the launchpads and to perform the REST operations.

You can use this API in your app when you want to get launchpad details, Delete the Launchpad, or create the new Launchpad. Launchpad holds the tile group and corresponding tile and apps details.

Every app must have the right roles (permissions) that enable access to the Launchpad, tile groups, tile, and app in your system.
